e best sprinters in the world.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2987352542723344e-21, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan\", \"score\": 0.9954741424816291, \"rank\": 0.004546434031048145, \"text\": \"Mandan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"the best sprinters\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, many times I look at it as close to 20 something years in training.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What kept me going is my family.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not just run from me,\\\" Blake said.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Blake\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nicknamed 'The Beast', 34-year-old Blake will race at his fourth edition of the Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999980913117, \"rank\": 1.9086911209977306e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P